{"id":440,"category_slug":"english-conversations","category_name":"Conversations","position":42,"title":"42. Would You Call me?","subtitle":"","level":"A2","parts":15,"url":"https://dailydictation.com/exercises/english-conversations/42-would-you-call-me.440/listen-and-type","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/42-would-you-call-me-2022-03-07-21-18-59/0-42-would-you-call-me.mp3","transcript":"Well, see you tomorrow.\nI'd better go, too.\nOh, would you do me a favour?\nSure.\nWould you call me tomorrow at six o'clock in the morning?\nTomorrow's my daughter's birthday. I wanna get her a new robe,\nand I have to pick up the dry cleaning, and pick up the cake from the bakery.\nAnyway, I have lots of things to do.\nBut I'm not sure I can get up early.\nDo you need a hand?\nOh, can you? That would be great.\nCan you go to the mall and buy her a new robe,\npick up the dry cleaning, and get the cake from the bakery?\nAnd what will you be doing?\nSleeping in of course!","youtube_video_id":"","details_cached_at":"2026-06-15T20:48:43","challenges":[{"position":1,"content":"Well, see you tomorrow.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/42-would-you-call-me-2022-03-07-21-18-59/1.mp3","time_start":2.62,"time_end":4.16},{"position":2,"content":"I'd better go, too.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/42-would-you-call-me-2022-03-07-21-18-59/2-2022-03-08-20-04-15.mp3","time_start":4.16,"time_end":5.3},{"position":3,"content":"Oh, would you do me a favour?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/42-would-you-call-me-2022-03-07-21-18-59/3.mp3","time_start":5.28,"time_end":6.52},{"position":4,"content":"Sure.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/42-would-you-call-me-2022-03-07-21-18-59/4.mp3","time_start":6.52,"time_end":7.06},{"position":5,"content":"Would you call me tomorrow at six o'clock in the morning?","audio_url":"https:/